data.description:
Beautifully Remodeled 4-Bed, 2-Bath Haven with High-End Kitchen  Charming Backyard Oasis!
Welcome to this stunningly remodeled and move-in ready 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home, complete with a spacious dining room, a versatile 10' x 9' office, and a convenient 1-car garage. The kitchen is a true showstopper, having undergone a high-end renovation in 2020 that will leave you in awe.
Experience the ultimate in functionality and style with custom soft-close cabinets, blind-corner pullouts, pull-out pantry and trash cabinets, all topped off with gorgeous quartz countertops and a breakfast bar equipped with swivel stools for added comfort and convenience.
As you explore the main living areas, you'll be delighted by the fine details, including beautiful custom 8 Alderwood baseboard and fresh paint, creating an inviting ambiance throughout the home. Say goodbye to carpet cleaning woes, as the recently refinished hardwood floors and luxury vinyl plank flooring grace every corner of this exquisite dwelling.
The clever blend of modern colors with warm wood accents creates a perfect harmony that will surely captivate your heart. Draw open the brand-new blinds and let the sunlight flood the rooms, offering picturesque views of the lush greenery outside. Alternatively, step onto the large back deck, which is pre-plumbed for a gas grill, making it the ideal spot for outdoor entertainment.
The charm extends beyond the home's interior, with a generously sized lot boasting mature landscaping both in the front and backyards. Take advantage of the in-ground sprinklers and ample shade provided by large trees. In addition, your very own peach tree, apple tree, and small garden await you, promising a delightful experience for any green thumb enthusiast.
Don't miss the opportunity to make this gem your own, as it is sure to attract keen interest. Come by and see for yourself the wonders this home has to offer, but be quick  this beauty won't stay on the market for long!
Lifestyle in Montezuma County, Colorado
Discover the allure of Montezuma County, Colorado, a hidden gem nestled amidst breathtaking natural beauty. Located in the heart of the Four Corners region, this enchanting destination offers a diverse array of attractions and activities for every adventurer.
Explore the ancient mysteries of Mesa Verde National Park, where you can marvel at the well-preserved cliff dwellings of the Ancestral Pueblo people. Embark on outdoor escapades in the San Juan National Forest, where lush forests, majestic mountains, and sparkling lakes await exploration.
Montezuma County is a haven for history enthusiasts, with its rich cultural heritage evident in the charming towns and museums that dot the landscape. Delight in the local art scene and immerse yourself in the authentic southwestern charm of the area.
Indulge in farm-to-table dining experiences, savoring the flavors of fresh produce and local cuisine. The region's welcoming community and vibrant events will make you feel right at home.
Whether you seek outdoor adventures, cultural experiences, or a peaceful escape, Montezuma County beckons with its captivating blend of nature, history, and charm. Uncover the wonders of this captivating Colorado destination and create memories that will last a lifetime. Plan your visit today!
